                                                              [21 March 81]
Lieber David

.ue 2
                                                                      $..#$
Forts.: 21 March 81
Ganz recht come on Saturd with Marie and Willy. Our Mary is pretty well.
Perhaps Feddy tells you that something is to be talked through <Tantes
Geld>*. So come for dinner if possible

                               Hearty kisses
.fo -
                                         from Pa
21 March 81
